Sarah Beasley

Bio

I am a 5th year, PY3 PharmD student at MCPHS University who has recently obtained my Minor in Biostatistics from Simmons University. My research interests involve R&D for new and promising drugs with a focus on overall clinical development, integrating my knowledge of clinical care towards a better future for healthcare. I am currently looking for opportunities that allow me to expand my knowledge of pharmacy through practice in different sub-fields to develop my critical thinking and leadership skills.
